<item>
            <title>[SOLR-686] single lock factory overwrites previous</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-686</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On a core reload, the Directory is retrieved and a new single lock factory is set, effectively removing all previous locks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
